# Production cron template. Install via the platform's scheduler
# (Kubernetes CronJob, Coolify scheduled jobs, Render Cron Jobs, etc.)
# Times are UTC.

# Hourly: nightly is not enough for a transactional store.
# Adjust to your RPO; the default targets ≤ 1 hour of data loss.
0 * * * *   /app/scripts/backup.sh /var/backups/offisdesign

# Daily 02:15 UTC: prune retired carts and audit older than 90 days.
15 2 * * *  curl -fsS -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer ${OPS_TOKEN}" \
              "${API_PUBLIC_URL}/v1/admin/ops/cleanup/run"

# Hourly: reconcile abandoned-checkout state.
30 * * * *  curl -fsS -X POST -H "Authorization: Bearer ${OPS_TOKEN}" \
              "${API_PUBLIC_URL}/v1/admin/ops/abandoned-checkout/scan"
